creator: IB Exchange Corp.
descriptionHtml:
Trade with your mobile and tablet on the app based version of the Mexem Global Trading. You have access to the stock markets and your personal account at any given moment. Trade in stocks, options, structured products, futures, currencies and more.
You can log in via this app when you are customer of MeXeM. Don’t have an account yet? Take our mobile platform for a test drive: no registration is required to log in and view unlimited delayed quotes.
Our mobile trading platform features include:
* Access to real-time streaming quotes and charts
* BookTrader Trading Tool
* Real-time Market Scanners
* Real-time Alerts with email notification
* Delayed market data for non-subscribed tickers and non-IB customers
* Support for trading stocks, options, futures, futures options and forex worldwide
* The ability to route orders using IB's SmartRouting℠ technology, which searches for the best price and dynamically routes and re-routes all or part of your order to achieve optimal execution
* Quick access to trade reports, portfolio and account information
* Secure login through IB's Secure Login System
* Access to Daily IB Market Briefs
* Free customer support- Scan and find new opportunities with the mobile scanner
* Monitor your orders, portfolio and current positions in real-time
descriptionShort: Trade with your mobile on the app based version of the Mexem Global Trading.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
﻿It's now easier than ever to find a product to trade. Smart filtering with type-ahead technology lists the best-matching products as you start to type a symbol or company name, prioritizing those for which you have trading permissions. Tap a product to add it to your screen.
Stability and reliability fixes.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
﻿Use the built-in Tax Optimizer to match closing trades to different open lots to change the cost basis for a trade. Changing the lots that are used for closing transactions can potentially change what you owe (or can deduct) at tax time.
Post-trade improvements let you immediately see the status of recently submitted orders, along with next-step action buttons like Create Alert and more. Tap the Exit Strategy button for a working order or current positions.

Trade with your mobile and tablet on the app based version of the Mexem Global Trading. You have access to the stock markets and your personal account at any given moment. Trade in stocks, options, structured products, futures, currencies and more.
You can log in via this app when you are customer of MEXEM. Don’t have an account yet? Take our mobile platform for a test drive: no registration is required to log in and view unlimited delayed quotes.
Our mobile trading platform features include:
* Access to real-time streaming quotes and charts
* BookTrader Trading Tool
* Real-time Market Scanners
* Real-time Alerts with email notification
* Delayed market data for non-subscribed tickers and non-IB customers
* Support for trading stocks, options, futures, futures options and forex worldwide
* The ability to route orders using IB's SmartRouting℠ technology, which searches for the best price and dynamically routes and re-routes all or part of your order to achieve optimal execution
* Quick access to trade reports, portfolio and account information
* Secure login through IB's Secure Login System
* Access to Daily IB Market Briefs
* Free customer support- Scan and find new opportunities with the mobile scanner
* Monitor your orders, portfolio and current positions in real-time
descriptionShort: Trade with your mobile on the app based version of the Mexem Global Trading.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: ﻿The Quote Info Bar, now shown just below an asset’s price in the Quote Details screen, uses icons to relay additional information such as higher than usual margin requirements, no Shortable inventory, additional trading permissions or available market data subscriptions.

﻿Put your favorite investments on autopilot with recurring investments in the stocks and ETFs of your choice. Tap “Recurring” in the Trade Launchpad to create investment schedules.
Streamlined Quote Details includes Overflow Menu with full list of actions.

Added overnight trading for US stocks.
News & Research tool lets you filter by news type, follow feeds, save Advanced Search as a personal feed, tag to “read later” and more!
Navigation improvements in Settings and Overflow menus. Scanners and Calendars now accessible from search, Portfolio tabs can be reorganized.
Reworked Login screen.
QR code support added for alternative key authentication.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Conditional orders automatically submit or cancel your order if your defined criteria are met. Set conditions on price, change %, volume, margin cushion, another instrument being traded, etc.
New Portfolio tabs now consolidate all position-related account and orders content in one place!
Check out the new Markets page to discover trading opportunities through news, upcoming events, or market movement.
We have replaced the Navigation menu with the new Account menu.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Introducing One-Cancels-Another (OCA) orders. From the order ticket, place two or more orders where if one order fills, the others are automatically cancelled or reduced. With OCA orders, you can create complex trading strategies and find the perfect opportunity to enter or exit the market.
